/*
:name: pipe_state_acc
:type: equiv
:verilog_top: pipe_state_acc.acc_mix
:pyrope_top: acc_mix
*/

// 2d-reg — the 06c `acc_mix` analog (wrap-free by bounding instead of
// `wrap`): tmp reads its own q => state register, home stage 0; mixing
// state q with the current input is coherent (both sigma=0). The pipe[1]
// inserted output flop keeps its full depth (body sigma=0).
//
// Widths are kept deliberately small (u8 state, u4 inputs): the v2prp
// direction LECs prp-vs-prp through the cvc5 BMC engine, whose cost grows
// with the state register's bit width, and a u20 accumulator made that
// check take ~60s. u8 keeps the SAME structural property under test while
// the BMC stays well under the harness timeout. Still wrap-free:
// `tmp < 200` => tmp + a + b <= 199 + 15 + 15 = 229 <= 255 (u8 max).
pub pipe[1] acc_mix(a:u4, b:u4) -> (x:u9) {
  reg tmp:u8 = 0
  if tmp < 200 {
    tmp = tmp + a + b
  }
  x = tmp + a
}
